    public abstract class XmlPollingAvlModule
extends PollUrlAvlModule
    Polls XML feed for AVL data. To be overridden with subclass that specifies URL to use and how to process the data. If in playback then feed will not be run since will be getting AVL data from db instead of from AVL feed.
